      ],
      "skos:definition": "M0 ontologies representing actual deployed systems analyzed using TSCG framework. These are not pedagogical examples but real applications with stakeholders.",
      "rdfs:comment": "Real-World Systems demonstrate TSCG applied to production environments. May be complex (non-minimal) and evolving. Used to validate TSCG scalability beyond simple examples.",
